  Value     Meaning
  --------  --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  erAbort   Aborts the entire \search operation; Search will return with result False.
  erIgnore  Aborts the \search operation in the directory where the error occurred, and
              continues in the next.
  erRaise   Raises a system error.
